name: 100 PLANKS
description:
A popular starter kit to ‘test the enthusiasm’ of the recipient. 
With no small parts or glue required PLANKS are suitable for even the smallest of builders.  

Identical in size and shape, and cut precisely from 100% farmed pine, each plank is long enough to counter balance, thin enough to stack and heavy enough to weigh structures down; holding together the most amazing creations.

PLANKS by Green Hat Workshop are specifically designed so that each side is evenly relative to the next. This precision means that with the help of gravity, a little imagination, passion and skill you can build, boats and castles, animals and robots, cities and forests, or even a spiraling staircase to the moon.

PLANKS can be used to create both simple and more complex structures; by their very nature they provide challenge and engagement for builders of all ages and abilities. For the young, and the young at heart, PLANKS are great for individual or group play allowing you to build your own architecturally designed masterpiece or work together to create the ideal city or fantasy land.

PLANKS are a rare construction resource that authentically engages all ages. Safe enough for newborns to pound together and engaging enough for grownups to get involved in the experimentation and suspenseful play that these dynamic building blocks afford.

PLANKS are both playful and educational, allowing children to experience and negotiate a wide range of important social skills; encouraging players to understand and explore the ideas and processes of mathematics and science in a creative way.

Why Build with PLANKS?

There are a range of reasons why people should spend time building with PLANKS, not the least of which is that it is incredibly fun and building something enormous or intricate can be very rewarding.

Benefits of building include:
-It develops group cooperation and improved communication skills.
-Using PLANKS develops an understanding of structural design and develops innovation.
-Many of the natural skills of our children, which provide self esteem are lost in the time restraints of schools or not valued by the curriculum. Here is an intuitive activity which provides countless opportunities for success.
-Impressive projects need not be limited to those with well honed architects. The open ended nature of plank block building allows anyone to work with the basic forms to create something remarkable.
-In a world where most games and activities have a defined goal and educative/play experiences are provided more and more as tabloid highlights, it is nice to find an activity which stimulates concentration, where you define the activity as you go.

Whether you are a toddler learning balance and 3D organisation for the first time, or a highly paid engineer, PLANKS can fill hours of happy creation.

100 PLANKS are packaged in a sturdy cardboard box which doubles as convenient storage for your PLANKS.

name: 100 Coloured Planks
description:
Loved by children and adults, PLANKS are great for individual play or group activities, encouraging a wonderful mix of creativity and skill, social development and imagination.
Includes blue, red, green and yellow PLANKS.

name: Small - Cloth Nappies
description:
Not only are Baby Chilli Modern Cloth Nappies a fun and exciting way to spice up your baby’s behind, but they also reduce your footprint on the environment an SAVE YOU MONEY! They ar as simple to put on as a disposable but also have the added ‘cuteness’ factor. They are also more breathable so can assist with nappy rash and also feel more comfortable on bub. 

Every year billions of disposable nappies make their way into landfill, taking hundreds of years to decompose. MCN’s are reusable and while the initial outlay for them can seem large, over the life of just one child in nappies the savings become very obvious, factor in subsequent children and the savings are HUGE. You can also say goodbye to rushing to the shops for a late night nappy pick up as you have run out. 

For example: using disposables for a year for one child will cost you around $900 a year. Times that by the number of years one child is in nappies and they can cost well over $2000. 

To use MCN’s full time you will need around 18-24 which is 6-8 per day with time for drying.

Size Small

Small         3.5-6kgs

Medium      6-11kgs

Large         9-18kgs

If unsure size up not down.

name: Medium Cloth Nappies
description:
Not only are Baby Chilli Modern Cloth Nappies a fun and exciting way to spice up your baby’s behind, but they also reduce your footprint on the environment an SAVE YOU MONEY! They ar as simple to put on as a disposable but also have the added ‘cuteness’ factor. They are also more breathable so can assist with nappy rash and also feel more comfortable on bub. 

Every year billions of disposable nappies make their way into landfill, taking hundreds of years to decompose. MCN’s are reusable and while the initial outlay for them can seem large, over the life of just one child in nappies the savings become very obvious, factor in subsequent children and the savings are HUGE. You can also say goodbye to rushing to the shops for a late night nappy pick up as you have run out. 

For example: using disposables for a year for one child will cost you around $900 a year. Times that by the number of years one child is in nappies and they can cost well over $2000. 

To use MCN’s full time you will need around 18-24 which is 6-8 per day with time for drying.

description:
